3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely category as the paper proposes a new method for generating personalized in-painting results using exemplar information. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the task of in-painting in natural pictures, which is a common problem in computer graphics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with the task of in-painting in images, which is a common problem in multimedia applications.
